enable dissemination to a broad audience in classrooms and elsewhere. The game was part of the tools
developed in the framework of the LearnML Erasmus+ project. A preliminary online survey was used to gauge
how well the game was received by teachers and students, with an overall positive result. A longer-term data
collection of the game usage statistics has been initiated and will be analysed over the course of the game
dissemination.},
